    "##### 13.\tApply feature selection using Information Gain ratio\n",
    "пГЉ\tCalculate the information gain of each feature of the iris dataset <br>\n",
    "пГЉ\tSelect the best 2 features of the iris dataset <br>\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
